cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.IR. 

The paper focuses on multi-person tracking in surveillance videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of face recognition and appearance modeling also suggests a potential fit for machine learning (cs.MM) and statistical learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The challenges of long-term tracking and the need for video summarization also suggest potential fits for cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
